# Everything in this repo that supports the website or development, and which
# should NOT be copied into a user's project by
# `quarto use template jhelvy/quarto-lexis`. Providing this file replaces
# Quarto's built-in defaults, so the dot-files and README have to be listed too.
#
# What's left — `_extensions/`, `template.qmd`, `images/` — is the template.

.git/
.gitignore
.quartoignore
.nojekyll
.quarto/
.Rproj.user/

README.md
README.qmd
PROJECT-BRIEF.md
build.R

index.qmd
index.css
index.html
index_files/

_description.qmd
_install.qmd
_conventions.qmd
_footer.qmd

lexis-template/
starting-assets/
